Package: digger
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, bind9-dnsutils
Description: Modern DNS lookup tool for GNOME
 A powerful and modern DNS lookup tool built with Vala, GTK4 and
 libadwaita. Digger provides an intuitive interface for DNS queries
 with batch lookups, server comparison, DNSSEC validation and
 DNS-over-HTTPS support.
